{"tid":1576571,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"HKCC 促請各個莊履行承諾於 本星期內 退還OCAMP已繳款項","createTime":"2019-09-17T09:58:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-20T12:54:09.000Z","uid":312966,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"1fe2c436171df25e3efd2352746b5d053452d021","tid":1576571,"uid":312966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T09:58:04.000Z","msg":"各個莊員早前承諾會於<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">本星期一</span></span>完成ocamp退款的手續，現時回覆因事務繁忙而未能進行退款，仍有數十位成員依然未獲退款的通知。<br />\n<br />\n促請所有莊員盡快處理退款事宜。<br />\n<br />\n某莊亦在早前聲稱本人的指控有造謠的成分，現時事情已得到確認，並無造謠成份，該莊的聲明書嚴重損害本人的聲譽，本人將保留追究的權利。<br />\n<br />\n650 缺一不可<br />\n光復fm cc革命<br />\n<br />\n以下附上部分來自莊員的回覆證明。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/efCsVbM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FefCsVbM.jpg&h=a7ec89fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OkC4Xp5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOkC4Xp5.jpg&h=e3aa97cc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cc6e0b72c8d3db1f916e0b3c7c5dc4b53a36fc00","tid":1576571,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T09:58:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yt2HG33.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fyt2HG33.jpg&h=9fcb0aae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TrPZKfU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTrPZKfU.jpg&h=433e1fe6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【922攻略流出】<br />\n907<span style=\"color: gold;\">加強版</span>配合hkmap live <br />\n更「大局」交通測試，彩虹戰衣、影帝、機巴、塞鐵、嶄新突擊RB、私家車傾巢而出，裡應外合 <br />\n+機場員工集體Call Sick <br />\n+雷達站/機場附近新搞作<br />\n+大量中港貨櫃司機加入物資支援！<br />\n<br />\n更多攻略，陸續公布，敬請留意"},{"pid":"1480f07904254ff82c13f5851602c351fd812e04","tid":1576571,"uid":313452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T10:02:56.000Z","msg":"回水 回水 回水"},{"pid":"719ec186c9f0c045b5f0a99c44246109cc0a1e1a","tid":1576571,"u